      "text": "Un preekſch winna Azzim\\\ntappe Baālimu Altari falausiti/ 2\\\nun tahṣ Bildes/ kas wiſit us\\\nteem bija/ nozirte wiſch/ ir tohs\\\nElka Meschus/ un tahṣ iſgree-\\\nftas un leetas Bildes falausfia\\\nwiſch/ un darrija tahṣ par\\\nPihſchleem/ un kaitija tohs us\\\nto paſchu Rappeemi/ kas tahin\\\nbij uppureiſchi.\n"
